# Delivery workflow

- Start from the relevant Architecture Bible chapter, ADRs, and `docs/PROJECT_BIBLE.md`.
- Define one bounded outcome and its acceptance criteria before editing.
- Inspect the worktree and preserve unrelated changes.
- Implement the smallest complete slice, then run proportionate checks.
- Update documentation and ADRs in the same change when contracts or decisions change.
- Use focused commits and the branch conventions in `CONTRIBUTING.md`.
- Hand off with scope, verification, risks, and follow-up work stated clearly.
